{"article_id":"AeAO1pBfCd56Zl99","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump stormed out of talks with Democratic congressional leaders on Wednesday over funding for a border wall with Mexico","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and reopening the government ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"complaining","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"the meeting at the White House was \" a total waste of time . \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"On the 19th day of a partial government shutdown","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"caused by the dispute over the wall ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"a short meeting","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"that included Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"House of Representatives Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"ended in acrimony with no sign of a resolution .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"\" Just left a meeting with Chuck and Nancy , a total waste of time , \"","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"\" I asked what is going to happen in 30 days","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"if I quickly open things up ,","depth":14},{"id":15,"text":"are you going to approve Border Security","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"which includes a Wall or Steel Barrier ? \"","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"\" Nancy said ,","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"NO .","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"I said","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"bye-bye ,","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"nothing else works ! \"","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"Exasperated Democrats called Trump ' s behavior a \" temper tantrum \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"the meeting broke down","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"when they refused to commit to funding his proposed southern border wall .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Trump ' s desire for a wall between the United States and Mexico was a central theme of his 2016 presidential campaign .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"\" It was a petulant president of the United States , \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Pelosi told reporters","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"when she returned to the Capitol .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"\" A person","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who would say :","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"' I ' ll keep government shut down for weeks , months or years","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"unless I get my way. '","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"That ' s just not the way","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"democracy works ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and so it ' s very sad . \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Schumer said","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Trump had had \" a temper tantrum. \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"The lawmaker told reporters :","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" That is sad and unfortunate .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"We want to come to an agreement .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"We believe in border security .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"We have different views . \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The breakdown in talks could strengthen the possibility","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that Trump will declare a national emergency","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to build a wall on the southern border","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"if no deal with Congress can be reached on his request for $ 5.7 billion for the project .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Earlier on Wednesday , Trump said","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"he had the authority","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to declare a national emergency","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that would let him pay for the wall with military funds .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence told reporters","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Trump was still considering that option .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Asked what Trump had gained","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"by walking out ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Pence said :","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the president made his position very clear today :","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that there will be no deal","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"without a wall . \"","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Shortly after the White House meeting broke up ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"the Democratic-controlled House of Representatives passed legislation","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"to end a partial shutdown of the Treasury Department and some other agencies","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"that have been closed since Dec. 22 ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"without money for the wall .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"But there was no indication","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"controlled by Trump ' s fellow Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"would allow a vote on the bill .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Democrats are eager to force Republicans to choose between funding the Treasury ' s Internal Revenue Service","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"- at a time","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"when it should be gearing up","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"to issue tax refunds to millions of Americans -","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"and voting","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to keep it partially shuttered .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"In a countermove , the Trump administration said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"even without a new shot of funding ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"the IRS would somehow make sure","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"those refund checks get sent .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"The National Treasury Employees Union filed suit on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"challenging the administration ' s authority","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to force federal employees to work","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"without pay .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump talks to reporters","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"as Vice President Mike Pence looks on","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"as the president departs","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"after addressing a closed Senate Republican policy lunch","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"while a partial government shutdown enters its 19th day on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S. , January 9 , 2019 .","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"/Jim Young","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Trump attended a lunch meeting of Senate Republicans on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"and emerged","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"to declare unwavering support for the tough stance","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"he has taken","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"on funds for the wall .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Asked if he got the impression in the meeting","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that the shutdown would end soon ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Republican Senator Tim Scott said :","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"\" I did not .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"we ' re going to be here a while . \"","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Pelosi plans more votes this week","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"that one by one would provide money","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"to operate departments","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"ranging from Homeland Security and Justice to State , Agriculture , Commerce and Labor .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Able to get the bills through the House","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"because of the Democratic majority ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Pelosi is hoping","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"some Senate Republicans back her up","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"and abandon Trump ' s wall gambit .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"The political maneuvering comes amid a rising public backlash over the suspension of government activities","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"that has resulted in the layoffs of hundreds of thousands of federal workers .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Other \" essential \" employees are being required to report to work , but without pay for the time being .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"On Thursday , Trump travels to the border","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"to highlight what he calls an immigration \" crisis. \"","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"He delivered his first prime-time television address from the Oval Office on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"to make his case for the border wall .","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"The funding fight stems from Congress ' inability","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"to complete work by a deadline last September","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"on funding all government agencies .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"It did , however , appropriate money for about 75 percent of the government on time","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"- mainly military and health-related programs .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"U.S. airport security workers and air traffic controllers","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"working without pay","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"have warned","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that security and safety could be compromised","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"if the shutdown continues ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"but the Trump administration said","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"staffing was adequate","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"and travelers had not faced unusual delays .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Union officials said","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"some TSA officers had already quit","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"because of the shutdown","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"and many were considering quitting .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Ratings agency Fitch warned","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"that it could cut the U.S. triple-A sovereign debt credit rating later this year","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"if the shutdown proves prolonged","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"and Congress fails to raise the legal limit on the national debt in a timely manner .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":279,"left":0,"right":278,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":230,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"l